## Configuration

### Service Configuration

Services can be configured with:

- Base URLs per environment
- Authentication methods
- Custom headers
- Request timeouts

### Supported Authentication

- Bearer Token (JWT)
- API Key (custom header)
- Basic Authentication
- No Authentication

